<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Analytical Insight. Emotional Growth. | Therapy with [Your Name]</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --slate: #2c3e50;
            --sage: #9eb2a0;
            --cream: #f9f7f2;
            --gold: #b08d57;
        }
        body { font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--slate); margin: 0; background: var(--cream); }
        header { padding: 4rem 2rem; text-align: center; background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
        .container { max-width: 900px; margin: auto; padding: 2rem; }
        h1 { font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 0; }
        .tagline { color: var(--sage); font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
        .bio-section { display: flex; gap: 2rem; align-items: center; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .bio-photo { width: 300px; height: 400px; background: #ddd; border-radius: 4px; object-fit: cover; }
        .content { flex: 1; min-width: 300px; }
        .methodology { background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; margin: 3rem 0; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .cta-button { display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 2rem; background: var(--slate); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px; transition: 0.3s; margin-top: 1rem; }
        .cta-button:hover { background: var(--gold); }
        footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Precision Meets Insight</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Thoughtful, Strategic Therapy for Individuals and Couples</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
    <section class="bio-section">
        <img src="your-photo.jpg" alt="Therapist Portrait" class="bio-photo">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>The Analytical Lens</h2>
            <p>Before becoming a therapist, I spent years as an <strong>actuary</strong>—a profession grounded in precision and long-range thinking. Today, I bring that same intellectual curiosity to the human experience.</p>
            <p>I specialize in identifying the hidden patterns beneath the surface of your life, helping you determine when to listen to emotions and when to challenge them.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="methodology">
        <h3>Why This Approach?</h3>
        <p>If you feel "stuck" or misunderstood, standard talk therapy might not be enough. We will work to harness emotional insight with the goal of living with <strong>authenticity and intention</strong>. My approach is for those who want to stop living the life others expect and start living their own.</p>
        <center><a href="mailto:your-email@example.com" class="cta-button">Book a Consultation</a></center>
    </section>
</div>

<footer>
    &copy; 2026 [Your Name], Registered Psychotherapist. | [Your Registration #] | Toronto, ON
</footer>

</body>
</html>
